                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72/2162</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Denmark</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_EMF1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Egan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-09-28T17:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 28, 1915, 5 p. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 8.10 p. m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>174. I am credibly informed that through secret methods British destruction of
                    German submarine boats shows remarkable progress. Evident German alarm.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">American Minister</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
